# Insights

## Source of truth

- Grain / credit / fact contract: `docs/Database_Outline.md` (Insights / grain sections)
- Product priority & open rethink: `docs/Status.md` — do **not** invent a new analytics IA
- Implementation: `src/lib/insights.ts`, `src/screens/insights/`

## Locked model (day-one MVP)

- **Lens** = group-by grain (PG / category / muscle / session / block / sequence label).
- **Filters** = narrow the set (session label, block label, set type, Variations, Tools, dates).
- **Credit-each** for multi-tag grains (PG / category / muscle): a set can contribute to more than one bucket.
- **Honest partition** for nest-label lenses and once-totals (sessions, working sets, tonnage): count each set once.
- **Complete logs only** — incomplete sessions stay out of Insights aggregates.

## Do not

- Redesign Insights product surface unless Status / the user asks — rethink is still open.
- Point the app at `v_log_set_facts` unless that parked item is actively picked up (joins stay on `log_sets` today).
- Paste or rewrite design docs into rules; open the outline / Status instead.
